LUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts63" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts68" ANNOTATION_ID="a2834798"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Aber das ist ja klar.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts68" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts76" ANNOTATION_ID="a2834800"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Dann ist Alleinsein nicht schlimm.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts77" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts95" ANNOTATION_ID="a2834811"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Als ich damals in den Kindergarten kam, wusste ich noch nichts.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts95" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts120" ANNOTATION_ID="a2834812"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Ich spielte mit hörenden Kindern und kann mich nicht an Unterschiede zwischen Hörenden und Gehörlosen erinnern.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts120" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts137" ANNOTATION_ID="a2834816"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>So ging es weiter, bis ich in den Kindergarten in Halberstadt kam.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts137" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts158" ANNOTATION_ID="a2834850"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Das war interessant, ich war fasziniert von den Gebärden und wir spielten zusammen, das war klasse.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts158" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts165" ANNOTATION_ID="a2834853"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Ja, wir haben gespielt.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts165" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts172" ANNOTATION_ID="a2834856"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Ich habe schöne Erinnerungen an früher.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts172" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts191" ANNOTATION_ID="a3040803"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Wir haben gespielt und Quatsch gemacht, verschiedenes ausgeheckt, bis/</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts191" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts210" ANNOTATION_ID="a2834865"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Ja, die Zeit verging da so schnell, schon war ich eingeschult.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts210" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts223" ANNOTATION_ID="a2834886"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Ich musste dort zum Mathe- und Deutschunterricht und so weiter.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts223" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts248" ANNOTATION_ID="a2834925"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Ich war im Unterricht ganz gut, aber weil ich meistens mit den anderen zusammen spielte, verpasste ich einiges.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts248" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts265" ANNOTATION_ID="a2834913"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>So ging es ungefähr 10 Jahre lang, das war schön.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts266" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts299" ANNOTATION_ID="a2834966"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Den meisten Kontakt hatte ich mit einem, der durch und durch gehörlos ist, weil er der Sohn von gehörlosen Eltern ist.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts299" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts332" ANNOTATION_ID="a2834996"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Wir sind zusammen aufgewachsen, bis zu seiner Entlassung als Geselle waren wir immer zusammen, aber jetzt gehen wir jeweils unseren eigenen Lebensweg.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts334" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts349" ANNOTATION_ID="a2835023"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Na ja, gehörlos zu sein hat so seine Nachteile.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts349" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts378" ANNOTATION_ID="a2835037"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Ich kann die Welt nicht so erleben wie ein Hörender und mit anderen Hörenden kommunizieren. Da stoße ich immer auf Barrieren.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts378" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts401" ANNOTATION_ID="a2835057"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Und wenn ich mir zum Beispiel einen Film oder Infos anschauen will, sind die meist ohne Untertitel.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts401" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts408" ANNOTATION_ID="a2856590"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Das Gesprochene ist mühsam.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts408" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts431" ANNOTATION_ID="a2835080"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Oder ein anderes Beispiel: in der Disco gibt es viele hübsche Frauen, die ich gerne kennengelernt hätte.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts431" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts446" ANNOTATION_ID="a2934250"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Ich bedauere, dass ich sie mir nicht angeln kann, weil die Kommunikation ein Problem ist.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts446" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts449" ANNOTATION_ID="a2934251"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Das ist mühsam.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts449" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts452" ANNOTATION_ID="a2835093"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Oder/</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts452" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts462" ANNOTATION_ID="a2835095"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Ach, es gibt viele weitere Nachteile.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts463" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts490" ANNOTATION_ID="a2835181"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Oh, und ein Nachteil ist auch, dass ein Hörender es typischerweise mit dem Lernen viel leichter hat.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts490" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts499" ANNOTATION_ID="a3040643"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Er braucht nur zuzuhören und muss nicht noch viel lernen/</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts499" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts518" ANNOTATION_ID="a2835195"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Ich, als Gehörloser, muss viel lesen und verstehe viele Wörter nicht.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts518" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts521" ANNOTATION_ID="a3040649"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Das macht mir zu schaffen.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts521" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts528" ANNOTATION_ID="a2835200"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Das Lesen ist echt mühsam.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts528" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts535" ANNOTATION_ID="a2835202"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Das ist der typische Nachteil für einen Gehörlosen.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts535" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts542" ANNOTATION_ID="a2835208"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Aber was wäre ein Vorteil?</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts542" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts555" ANNOTATION_ID="a2835217"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Interessant ist, dass wir viel Mimik einsetzen und lachen.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts555" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts566" ANNOTATION_ID="a2856608"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Die Hörenden dagegen haben keine Mimik, das ist bei denen so gehaltlos.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts566" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts580" ANNOTATION_ID="a2835220"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Und was ist noch gut oder interessant am Gehörlossein, hm?</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts580" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts587" ANNOTATION_ID="a2835225"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Was sind noch andere Vorteile?</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts587" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts596" ANNOTATION_ID="a2835237"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Ja, wir hören nichts und haben so unsere Ruhe.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts596" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts611" ANNOTATION_ID="a2856610"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Hörende werden nervös oder bekommen Ohrenschmerzen. Die Ruhe ist ein Vorteil.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts611" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts626" ANNOTATION_ID="a2835238"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Noch mehr Vorteile sehe ich sonst nicht.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts628" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts635" ANNOTATION_ID="a2835245"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Schlechte Erfahrungen?</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts637" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts652" ANNOTATION_ID="a2835251"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Mein größtes Problem war mit meinen Eltern.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts652" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts670" ANNOTATION_ID="a2835253"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Denn ich wünschte mir so sehr, dass meine Eltern die Gebärdensprache können.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts670" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts679" ANNOTATION_ID="a2835282"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Aber sie taten nichts dafür.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts679" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts684" ANNOTATION_ID="a2835297"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Ich gebärde/</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts684" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts703" ANNOTATION_ID="a2856615"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Ich brauche zum Beispiel tiefgründige Unterhaltungen und den Austausch.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts703" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts718" ANNOTATION_ID="a2836121"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Dadurch habe ich bessere Lebenserfahrungen.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts718" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts731" ANNOTATION_ID="a2836144"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Aber von ihnen kam nichts, da musste ich selber aktiv werden. Das war mühsam.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts731" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts754" ANNOTATION_ID="a2836148"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Die gehörlosen Eltern meiner Freunde konnten mir vieles erklären, dafür bin ich ihnen sehr dankbar.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts754" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts760" ANNOTATION_ID="a2836163"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Mit meinen Eltern war es leider nicht so.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts760" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts787" ANNOTATION_ID="a2836164"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Und, na ja, es gab Probleme, über die ich mit ihnen reden wollte, aber das war schwer.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts787" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts798" ANNOTATION_ID="a2836165"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Sie verstanden mich nicht, das war sehr schwer für mich.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts798" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts821" ANNOTATION_ID="a2836179"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>In der Schule in Essen war das auch ein Problem, wir konnten schlecht mit den Lehrern kommunizieren.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts821" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts844" ANNOTATION_ID="a2836194"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Es gab Kommunikationsprobleme und Mobbing und ich habe mich geärgert, dass ich schlechte Noten bekommen habe, das war schwierig.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts844" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts857" ANNOTATION_ID="a2836210"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Es passierten viele schlimme Dinge. Ich war zum Beispiel in einer Gruppe, die schlimme Kritik ausgeteilt hat.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts857" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts868" ANNOTATION_ID="a2856630"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Ich habe mich auch ein bisschen geprügelt. Ach, das war schlecht.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts869" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts876" ANNOTATION_ID="a2836222"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>In Halberstadt gab es das nicht.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts876" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts883" ANNOTATION_ID="a2856634"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Da waren alle viel netter und freundlicher.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts883" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts902" ANNOTATION_ID="a2856642"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Aber in Essen war es richtig schlecht, also im Vergleich zu Essen war es in Halberstadt einfach besser.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts902" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts909" ANNOTATION_ID="a2836258"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Da ist es locker und man wird unterstützt.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts909" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts939" ANNOTATION_ID="a2856647"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Zum Beispiel sorgen sich die Lehrer um dich, wenn man Probleme hat, und sie helfen dir, unterstützen und fördern dich.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts939" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts954" ANNOTATION_ID="a2836264"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>In Essen ist das nicht so, da war ich auf mich alleine gestellt, so war das da.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts955" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts968" ANNOTATION_ID="a2836425"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Aber was jetzt gut war?</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts968" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts984" ANNOTATION_ID="a2836427"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Nicht wirklich, vieles war einfach gewöhnlich.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts985" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts992" ANNOTATION_ID="a2836432"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Ich/ Oh ja, das ist gut.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts992" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1008" ANNOTATION_ID="a2836433"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>In Essen konnte ich mehr Gehörlose kennenlernen.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1008" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1029" ANNOTATION_ID="a2856708"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Sie kamen von überall her zusammen, aus Hamburg, aus München oder aus Berlin, das war ganz verschieden.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1029" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1056" ANNOTATION_ID="a2836438"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Dort lernte ich andere Gebärden und wir tauschten gemeinsam unsere Lebenserfahrungen aus.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1056" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1075" ANNOTATION_ID="a2836440"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Dinge, von denen ich keine Ahnung hatte, wurden mir erklärt und ich verstand immer mehr.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1075" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1082" ANNOTATION_ID="a2836441"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Oder, was auch noch komisch war/</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1082" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1101" ANNOTATION_ID="a2856739"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Es gab auch eine tolle Kameradschaft, in der man sich locker austauschen konnte.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1101" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1122" ANNOTATION_ID="a2836444"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>In Essen war es einfach ASL zu lernen, im Osten gab es das nicht.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1122" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1140" ANNOTATION_ID="a2836446"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Dort, im Osten, wusste ich nicht viel über die Weltkultur.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1140" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1166" ANNOTATION_ID="a2836452"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Ja genau, ich bekam dort ASL-Unterricht und wurde darin besser.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1166" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1190" ANNOTATION_ID="a2836456"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Ja, oh, und in Essen war es so, dass man immer auf Partys eingeladen wurde, das war gut.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1190" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1225" ANNOTATION_ID="a2836467"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Ja, zusammen ist es besser. Zum Beispiel trennen sich jetzt wegen der Ausbildung oder der Arbeit unsere Lebenswege, nachdem wir in Essen in der Klasse zusammen waren.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1225" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1234" ANNOTATION_ID="a2836473"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Wenn man sich auf Gehörlosenpartys trifft, ist man dann endlich wieder zusammen.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1234" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1254" ANNOTATION_ID="a2856742"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Dennoch bin ich bis jetzt nicht so zufrieden wie in den drei Jahren in Essen.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1254" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1258" ANNOTATION_ID="a2836476"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Ja, so war es.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1260" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1274" ANNOTATION_ID="a2836479"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Gehörlose oder hörende Vorbilder?</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1274" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1286" ANNOTATION_ID="a2836482"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Hm, Vorbilder?</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1286" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1305" ANNOTATION_ID="a2836486"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Ja, es gibt einen Gehörlosen, der ist mein Vorbild.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1305" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1309" ANNOTATION_ID="a2856746"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Er ist aus Frankfurt.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1309" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1322" ANNOTATION_ID="a2836489"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Sein Verhalten und Charakter sind gut.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1322" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1336" ANNOTATION_ID="a2856747"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Er gebärdet sauber, benutzt viel Mimik und er ist nicht/</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1336" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1338" ANNOTATION_ID="a2856749"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Ja, ein Gehörloser.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1338" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1367" ANNOTATION_ID="a2837899"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Er verachtete niemanden mit niedrigem Niveau und brachte mir viel bei, ab da ging es mit mir bergauf.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1367" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1392" ANNOTATION_ID="a2837932"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Früher hatte ich noch einen anderen Charakter und habe mich anders verhalten, na ja.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1392" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1411" ANNOTATION_ID="a2837909"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Ich wusste noch nicht so viel, war noch nicht auf seinem Niveau, aber er brachte mir viel bei und ich wurde immer besser.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1411" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1428" ANNOTATION_ID="a2836496"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Dafür bin ich ihm dankbar und deshalb ist er mein Vorbild.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1430" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1441" ANNOTATION_ID="a2836502"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Nein, er kommt aus Frankfurt.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1441" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1452" ANNOTATION_ID="a2836503"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Ich lernte ihn durch meinen Umzug nach Essen kennen.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1452" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1467" ANNOTATION_ID="a2836504"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>In Halberstadt hat mir niemand was beigebracht.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1467" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1494" ANNOTATION_ID="a2836505"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Erst als ich nach Essen zog, lernte ich den Frankfurter und interessante Personen kennen, von denen ich etwas lernen konnte.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1496" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1499" ANNOTATION_ID="a2837944"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Aber/</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1499" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1507" ANNOTATION_ID="a2837955"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Ja, wir stehen noch im Kontakt.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1507" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1522" ANNOTATION_ID="a2837958"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Klar, wenn wir beide zufällig mal auf einer Party sind, sehen wir uns.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1522" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1538" ANNOTATION_ID="a2856752"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Wir schaffen es aber zeitlich nicht uns gegenseitig zu besuchen, das ist zu schwer.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1538" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1561" ANNOTATION_ID="a2837982"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Ja, das stimmt. Er wohnt in der Umgebung von Frankfurt, also nicht direkt in der Nähe, sondern etwas außerhalb.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1563" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1575" ANNOTATION_ID="a2837991"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Schöne Erinnerungen?</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1575" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1600" ANNOTATION_ID="a2837992"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Meistens in Essen, dort hatte ich viele schöne Erlebnisse, eben weil wir dort viel zusammen waren.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1600" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1609" ANNOTATION_ID="a2838005"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Im Internat konnten wir locker sein.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1609" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1622" ANNOTATION_ID="a2856755"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Im Internat kamen viele Gehörlose zusammen.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION></TIER><TIER TIER_ID="Translation_into_English_A" LINGUISTIC_TYPE_REF="L_text__coarser_granularity" PARTICIPANT="ber-36"><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts12" ANNOTATION_ID="a2943535"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>What my life looks like?</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts12" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts19" ANNOTATION_ID="a2943538"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Well, I grew up as a deaf person.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts19" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts40" ANNOTATION_ID="a2943545"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>If I imagine myself being all alone, I guess I would be feeling rather lonely.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts40" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts68" ANNOTATION_ID="a2943560"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>I'd obviously prefer meeting up with lots of other deaf people and doing something together - then, life is great.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts68" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts76" ANNOTATION_ID="a2943568"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Then, being alone isn't too bad.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts77" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts95" ANNOTATION_ID="a2943583"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>I didn't know anything about it when I first entered kindergarten.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts95" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts137" ANNOTATION_ID="a2943585"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>I played with the hearing children; I cannot remember seeing any differences between the hearing and the deaf children until I went to a kindergarten in Halberstadt.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts137" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts158" ANNOTATION_ID="a2943599"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>That was an interesting time. The signs fascinated me, and we all played together; it was awesome.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts158" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts165" ANNOTATION_ID="a2943604"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Yes, we played with each other.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts165" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts172" ANNOTATION_ID="a3040801"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>I have really fond memories of the past.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts172" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts191" ANNOTATION_ID="a3040805"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>We played a lot, joked around, plotted pranks and did stuff like that until/</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts191" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts210" ANNOTATION_ID="a2943619"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Well, time went by so fast - soon I attended first grade.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts210" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts223" ANNOTATION_ID="a2943622"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>I had to take classes in Math and German, and things like that.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts223" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts248" ANNOTATION_ID="a2943640"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>I was quite good at school. Yet, I missed quite a bit of the subject matter, because I mostly played with the other children.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts248" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts265" ANNOTATION_ID="a2943687"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>That's what it was like for approximately ten years. It was a wonderful time.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts266" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts299" ANNOTATION_ID="a2943734"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>I was closest to a boy who was Deaf to the core, because he was the son of deaf parents.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts299" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts332" ANNOTATION_ID="a2943751"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>We grew up around each other: we did everything together until he was done with his apprenticeship. Nowadays, we each follow our own independent paths.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts334" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts349" ANNOTATION_ID="a2943780"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Well, being deaf has its disadvantages for sure.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts349" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts378" ANNOTATION_ID="a2943786"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>I'm not able to perceive the world the way a hearing person would, and I cannot communicate well with hearing people. I always encounter difficulties when doing so.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts378" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts401" ANNOTATION_ID="a2943789"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>And if I want to watch a movie or some kind of informational stuff, most programs don't have captions.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts401" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts408" ANNOTATION_ID="a2943791"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>It's hard to understand spoken language.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts408" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts431" ANNOTATION_ID="a2943796"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Maybe another example: there are tons of lovely ladies at the club whom I would love to get to know.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts431" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts446" ANNOTATION_ID="a2943799"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>I pity myself for not being able to get with them, because communicating with each other is problematic.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts446" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts449" ANNOTATION_ID="a2943801"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>It's exhausting.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts449" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts452" ANNOTATION_ID="a2943802"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Or/</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts452" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts462" ANNOTATION_ID="a2943805"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Well, there are many more disadvantages.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts463" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts490" ANNOTATION_ID="a3040644"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Oh, another disadvantage is that a hearing person typically has less trouble with learning new things.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts490" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts499" ANNOTATION_ID="a3040645"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>They just have to listen without studying much more/</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts499" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts518" ANNOTATION_ID="a2943812"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>I, as a deaf person, have to read a lot, and I still don't understand many of the words.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts518" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts521" ANNOTATION_ID="a3040650"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>That gets to me.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts521" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts528" ANNOTATION_ID="a2943813"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Reading is tough.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts528" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts535" ANNOTATION_ID="a2943816"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>That's a typical disadvantage of being deaf.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts535" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts542" ANNOTATION_ID="a2943818"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Well, what could be an advantage?</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts542" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts555" ANNOTATION_ID="a2943820"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>It's interesting that we use a lot of facial expression, and we laugh a lot.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts555" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts566" ANNOTATION_ID="a2943824"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Hearing people seem to not use any facial expression; it's so shallow.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts566" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts580" ANNOTATION_ID="a2943829"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>What else is positive or interesting about being deaf?</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts580" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts587" ANNOTATION_ID="a2943831"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>What are some other advantages?</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts587" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts596" ANNOTATION_ID="a2943832"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Right, we cannot hear; therefore, we have some peace and quiet at all times.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts596" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts611" ANNOTATION_ID="a2943834"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Hearing people get nervous, or they get an earache. Silence is an advantage.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts611" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts626" ANNOTATION_ID="a2943835"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Other than that, I don't really see any advantages.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts628" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts635" ANNOTATION_ID="a2943838"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Any negative experiences?</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts637" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts652" ANNOTATION_ID="a2949084"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>I had the biggest trouble with my parents.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts652" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts670" ANNOTATION_ID="a2949085"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>I really wanted my parents to know sign language.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts670" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts679" ANNOTATION_ID="a2949087"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>But they didn't do anything to learn it.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts679" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts684" ANNOTATION_ID="a2949089"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>I sign/</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts684" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts703" ANNOTATION_ID="a2949090"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>For example, I need some communicative exchange and profound conversations.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts703" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts718" ANNOTATION_ID="a2949097"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>It makes my experience of life a better one.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts718" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts731" ANNOTATION_ID="a2949107"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Yet, my parents didn't do anything. I had to take action myself. It was exhausting.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts731" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts754" ANNOTATION_ID="a2949109"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>My friends' deaf parents taught me a lot - I am really thankful for that.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts754" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts760" ANNOTATION_ID="a2949110"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Sadly, it was different with my parents, though.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts760" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts787" ANNOTATION_ID="a2949112"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Well, there were some issues I would have liked to discuss with them, but it was really hard.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts787" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts798" ANNOTATION_ID="a2949114"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>They didn't understand what I was telling them. That was hard for me.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts798" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts821" ANNOTATION_ID="a2949115"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>It was the same problem with the school in Essen: We weren't able to communicate properly with the teachers.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts821" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts844" ANNOTATION_ID="a2949117"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>There were some problems communication-wise and with bullying, and I was upset, because I received bad grades. It was tough.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts844" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts857" ANNOTATION_ID="a2952249"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>A lot of bad things happened. I was, for instance, part of a group that was very vocal when criticizing others.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts857" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts868" ANNOTATION_ID="a2952250"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Sometimes I got into fights as well. Oh dear, that was bad.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts869" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts876" ANNOTATION_ID="a2949125"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Nothing like that happened in Halberstadt.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts876" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts883" ANNOTATION_ID="a2949128"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Everybody was so much nicer and friendlier.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts883" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts902" ANNOTATION_ID="a2949129"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Yet, my time in Essen was pretty bad. Well, compared to what it was like in Essen, Halberstadt wasn't half as bad.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts902" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts909" ANNOTATION_ID="a2949131"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>They are more laid-back there, and they support you.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts909" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts939" ANNOTATION_ID="a2949133"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>For example, the teachers care for you, and they help and support you.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts939" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts954" ANNOTATION_ID="a2949135"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>The situation was different in Essen; I was on my own - that's what it was like.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts955" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts968" ANNOTATION_ID="a2950705"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Well, what was positive?</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts968" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts984" ANNOTATION_ID="a2950706"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Nothing really. Everything was just average.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts985" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts992" ANNOTATION_ID="a2950708"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>I/ Well, yes, that's something positive.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts992" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1008" ANNOTATION_ID="a2950709"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>I was able to meet more deaf people in Essen.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1008" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1029" ANNOTATION_ID="a2950710"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>They came from everywhere to Essen - from Hamburg, from Munich, or from Berlin.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1029" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1056" ANNOTATION_ID="a2950711"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>I learned some new signs, and we exchanged our experiences in life.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1056" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1075" ANNOTATION_ID="a2950712"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Things I had never understood beforehand were explained to me, and I finally began to understand more and more.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1075" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1082" ANNOTATION_ID="a2950713"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Something else that was remarkable/</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1082" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1101" ANNOTATION_ID="a2950714"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>We had a great friendship: we could casually hang out and talk to each other.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1101" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1122" ANNOTATION_ID="a2950715"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>It was easy to learn ASL in Essen. Yet, you couldn't do so in East Germany.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1122" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1140" ANNOTATION_ID="a2950716"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>I didn't know much about the different cultures in the world while living in Eastern Germany.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1140" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1166" ANNOTATION_ID="a2950718"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Exactly, I took classes in ASL and started to get better.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1166" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1190" ANNOTATION_ID="a2950719"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Oh, and I was invited to parties all the time while living in Essen. That was great.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1190" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1225" ANNOTATION_ID="a2950721"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Right, it's better to be in good company. Now, even if we were in the same class in Essen, our lives take separate paths because of the different work places and apprenticeships we chose.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1225" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1234" ANNOTATION_ID="a2950722"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>But when being at Deaf parties, you finally meet again.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1234" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1254" ANNOTATION_ID="a2950724"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Yet, after all, I'm still not as happy as I used to be for the three years living in Essen.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1254" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1258" ANNOTATION_ID="a2950725"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Yes, that's right.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1260" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1274" ANNOTATION_ID="a2950728"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Deaf or hearing role models?</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1274" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1286" ANNOTATION_ID="a2950730"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Well, role models?</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1286" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1305" ANNOTATION_ID="a2950731"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Right, there is one deaf person who's my role model.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1305" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1309" ANNOTATION_ID="a2950733"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>He's from Frankfurt.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1309" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1322" ANNOTATION_ID="a2950734"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>He has a great attitude and personality.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1322" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1336" ANNOTATION_ID="a2950736"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>His signing is clear, and he uses a lot of facial expression, and he's not/</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1336" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1338" ANNOTATION_ID="a2950738"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Yes, he is deaf.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1338" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1367" ANNOTATION_ID="a2950739"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>He doesn't judge others on their level of knowledge, and he taught me a lot. Since then, things have been looking up for me.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1367" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1392" ANNOTATION_ID="a2950742"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Well, I used to have a different personality and behaved differently back then.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1392" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1411" ANNOTATION_ID="a2950743"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>I didn't know as much; I wasn't as sophisticated as he was, but he taught me a lot, and I improved quickly.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1411" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1428" ANNOTATION_ID="a2950744"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>I am really grateful for his effort; that's why he is my role model.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1430" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1441" ANNOTATION_ID="a2950745"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>No, he is from Frankfurt.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1441" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1452" ANNOTATION_ID="a2950747"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>I met him when I moved to Essen.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1452" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1467" ANNOTATION_ID="a2950748"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>No one taught me a thing in Halberstadt.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1467" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1494" ANNOTATION_ID="a2950749"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>I didn't meet the guy from Frankfurt and other interesting people from whom I could learn new things until I moved to Essen.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1496" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1499" ANNOTATION_ID="a2950751"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>But/</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1499" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1507" ANNOTATION_ID="a2950752"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Yes, we are still in touch.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1507" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1522" ANNOTATION_ID="a2950753"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Sure! We get to see each other if we coincidentally are at the same party.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1522" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1538" ANNOTATION_ID="a2950755"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Yet, we cannot manage to visit each other. Time-wise, it is too difficult.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1538" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1561" ANNOTATION_ID="a2950757"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Yes, he does. He lives in the Frankfurt area. Not right in the city, but close to it.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1563" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1575" ANNOTATION_ID="a2950759"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>My greatest memories?</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1575" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1600" ANNOTATION_ID="a2950760"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>They are mostly from the time in Essen. There, I experienced quite a bit, because we hung out a lot.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1600" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1609" ANNOTATION_ID="a2950761"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>We were able to act casually at the boarding school.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1609" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1622" ANNOTATION_ID="a2950762"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>There were so many deaf people at the boarding school.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION></TIER><TIER TIER_ID="Lexem_Geb&#xE4;rde_r_A" LINGUISTIC_TYPE_REF="L_tokens_right_left__finer_granularity" PARTICIPANT="ber-36"><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts3" ANNOTATION_ID="a2914979_1"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>SEHEN1*</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts4" TIME_SLOT_REF2=